 Fine Day || Lovely ||\n|-\n|2013\n|Sharkarasya Gajah|| Mother || {{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RaoYKyHEVXM |title=Sharkarasya Gajah - The kid who wanted an Elephant! &#124; Short Film &#124; By Rajesh Kumar Sharma - YouTube |format= |work= |accessdate=}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RaoYKyHEVXM |title=Sharkarasya Gajah - The kid who wanted an Elephant! &#124; Short Film &#124; By Rajesh Kumar Sharma - YouTube |format= |work= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n|2008\n|Zyme|| The prostitute||\n|-\n|}\n\n==TV/Online Shows==\n* B Positive\n* Lavender\n* Meet The Editors\n* News n Views\n* e Buz\n* Asianetnews.com\n* E Times\n* Morning Show\n* Chuttuvattam\n* Malayali Life Chit Chat\n* Kerala Talkies\n* M7News\n* HotNSour TV\n* Cinilife\n* Charutha\n* Varthaprabhatham\n* Chayakoottu\n* Meet My Guest\n* Jangospace\n\n; Reality shows\n*2018: [[Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 1)]]\n*2019: [[Boeing Boeing (TV series)|Boeing Boeing]]\n\n==TV Series==\n* Ente Manasputhri ([[Asianet]]) as Jennifer\n\n==Advertisements==\n* Girl Self Employed\n* Manorama Magazine\n\n==Albums==\n* Sreenandhanam\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Shankar, Hima}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian actresses]]\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category: Bigg Boss contestants]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toAsianet(link changed toAsianet (TV channel)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hima_Shankar"}
